| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-1401 — Recovery Inhibition (8base)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 6c4e3ae1-20da-528a-b5b7-397a3a39d8cc"
